Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, move it! Don't\Ndisturb the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us how you're handling the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this murder the work of the serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The victims, the Jopps, don't\Nhave children, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, the scene\Nlooks just like one of the serial killings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of middle-aged married couples that\Nare happening all across Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard that a special agent from the\Nconfederate detective agency is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this proof that this is one\Nof the serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be faster to just ask the confederate\Ndetective agency itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to leave a lot of space for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:00:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Mr. Kipper for Hamburg Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the investigator from the\Nconfederate detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this incident related to\Nthose serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kipper from Hamburg Talk, I'll\Nsay something special, just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.79,0:01:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This murder was done by the killer\Nof those middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! The suspect is the\NJapanese doctor, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks exactly like the serial killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.31,0:01:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.98,0:01:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.14,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamburg Talk is pretty influential\Naround here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So your article will spread to other\Npapers across the country, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:29.14,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(360,340)}Lunge's Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've become the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I knock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It would be best not to alarm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a courteous old couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been invited into the\Nliving room without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't suspect a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I sit on the couch for guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A few minutes later, the husband\Ndies on the floor over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't started to\Nmake any movements yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, she isn't in the living room yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She is making tea in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the tea is prepared, the wife is killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,which means that I have to take action soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I take out my knife, and while the\Nhusband is still confused, I stab him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband runs while holding\Nhis wound with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The next attack is aimed at\Nthe husband's right shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:04:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Another clumsy miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What an amateur I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband cries out for his wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the wife can't hear\Nhim from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hearing has been getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of your wife\Neasily after I've killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've caught up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The husband's left handprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I catch up to the husband\Nat this sideboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't deliver the final blow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I am five meters from\Nwhere the husband died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't I deliver the final blow here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the man who killed the Jopps?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking the people of the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If he shows up, treat him naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then contact me as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe something so horrible\Nhappened in a neighborhood like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Jopps were such kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I called out to her in the morning,\Nshe'd always respond cheerfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You called out to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hearing has been going bad\Nfor about a year now, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written in her doctor's reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She shouldn't have been\Nable to hear you say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have sensed me\Nsome other way and responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people of the neighborhood\Ndidn't know about her hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extraordinary to have come this\Nfar at such a young age, Mr. Giebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. The makers we sign contracts\Nwith just have pretty good cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my deepest condolences\Nfor losing your uncle and aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I didn't have any other\Nrelatives besides them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your aunt and uncle were childless,\Nthey must have been quite fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, as if I were their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you catch the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have a good hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the details well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... There were other\Ncases similar to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How much did you inherit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Jopps were very wealthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that have anything\Nto do with the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who\Nwould inherit the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the right time to\Nbe talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if companies seem to be spectacularly\Nsuccessful on the surface, there are\Noften poor managers underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many cases like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you accusing me of killing\Nthem for the inheritance?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You have a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You took your secretary and subordinates\Nout to eat. There are witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the killer. That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These last few days,\NI checked up on that nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At first glance, his company looks quite good,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but behind it all, their stockbrokers mess\Nup, and their financial state is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been thoroughly scouring that company.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really see this case as\Npart of the serial murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is printing our exclusive scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no relationship between this murder and the\Nprevious ones, it'll be a terrible miscommunication.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the work of a copycat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He made it look like one of\Nthe serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! I have to change the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just leave it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to write the story stating that\Nthe murder is one of the serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke. Why should\NI print false information?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm a journalist. You can't\Npressure me into doing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You said your name was Kipper, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you find her to be a fascinating woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you have such a caring family...\Na wonderful wife and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess such a fascinating woman would make\Nyou want to be unfaithful, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do as I say this time... no, \Nif you keep on doing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it, he'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting good things from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. They were a wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, did they have any foster children?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a child who was staying\Nthere for only a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They loved their nephew very much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how would you like another cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the man in the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in my house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The nephew of the Jopps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You must think I'm the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed them for the inheritance...\NThat's what you think, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that I have quite a few debts now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the money they left me\Nwould definitely save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not that type of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is that all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You treat me like a murderer\Nand then say, "Is that all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have somewhere I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to take back what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The police have called off the\Npeople following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here are treating you as innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then who do you think the killer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can catch that one man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The bloodstains over there mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't think this murder's\Nperpetrator was the Japanese doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a copycat of the couples' serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in this case that\Nwas missing in other cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The killer catches up to the victim here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He delivers the final blow all the way over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why did he hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At the scene of the crimes\Nof the man I've been chasing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been valuables stolen to make it seem\Nlike a robbery, but there's no feeling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to the site of the crime this\Ntime, however, there was a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.91,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He paused when he saw his and\Nhis victim's faces in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The police here are brainless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the doing of a copycat who\Nmade it look like Johan's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will this continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally meet, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for you for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So very long...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep\Ndoing this, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I get rid of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed the Jopps... Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, he'll die from blood loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did this to Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to leave him\Nin front of a hospital and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the keys to the handcuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother looking for your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where the keys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've looked at your wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The wound, fortunately, did not\Nreach your abdominal cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if I don't stop \Nthe bleeding, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The three murders at Eisler Memorial Hospital, the\Nserial killings of couples over the last three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You really will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all "Johan's" work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You were searching for the real killer, "Johan."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are Johan, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't much I could find\Nin this old warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I found materials for emergency treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If only my hands were free, I could save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're Dr. Tenma, you're\Nan exceptional surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That face of yours doesn't have\None speck of wickedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people have you\Nkilled with those hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you change into "Johan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you change into that killing machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The drop in blood pressure is making you\Nwaver in and out of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your crime scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't talk anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At your crime scenes, there's no feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You lose your emotions when you hold the lives\Nof people in your hands every day, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's there. That calmness is\Nalways at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Total calmness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I was performing surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed I wouldn't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed that it would go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I worried that there'd be problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that I was\Nscared out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,People's lives are in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could be calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop the bleeding. Where is the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it in your pants pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.92,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're complexion looks better now\Nthan when you're working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergency treatment was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the doctors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't have been done\Nso well, you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma... saved my life.\NThat's what happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Tenma might have gotten away,\Nbut... Giebel confessed to the murder of the Jopps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.57,0:21:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be hard for\Nhim to arrest Tenma now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We should take Lunge off of the Tenma case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry that Inspector Lunge\Ncaused you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't trouble at all.\NHe's very nice to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's in a hurry and would like to\Nget done with rehab as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already squeezing the ball\Nand walking around the halls...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He says it quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He says that he's never\Nhad so much fun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what did he say the killer's name was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chasing after a criminal like Tenma\Nis the most fun I can have."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.15,0:23:53.55,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Eva's Confession
